Rules-Requires-Root: binary-targets

Package: cerberus
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-venv, python3-yaml, systemd
Description: Periodic nginx vhost security monitor for Debian servers
 Cerberus scans nginx virtual hosts, detects application stacks,
 correlates local versions with a cached advisory database, and sends
 actionable alert emails only when findings are new or materially changed.
 .
 The Debian package installs the project under /opt/cerberus, creates a
 dedicated virtual environment under /opt/cerberus/.venv during postinst,
 and exposes stable admin-facing commands in /usr/local/bin/.
